==Non-player characters==
The following is a list of non-player characters that appear in ''Vampire Survivors'' (not counting all of the merchants that are also player characters, any [[enemy]], or any of the [[Characters/Unused|unused characters]]):
*'''{{slink|Eggman}}:''' a merchant in [[Moongolow]] who only sells {{slink|Golden Egg|txt=Golden Eggs}}.
*'''{{slink|Healer}}:''' a merchant in [[Moongolow]] who can remove {{slink|Golden Egg|txt=Golden Eggs}}.
*'''{{slink|Xanthia}}:''' a merchant who appears in [[Planar Bazaar]] where they sell the {{slink|Victory Sword}} and the {{slink|Phas3r}}. They also sell the {{slink|Emerald Disk}} and the {{slink|Joker Disk}} in [[Moongolow]].
*'''{{slink|Giocare}}:''' a merchant in [[Westwoods]] who asks for the player to spin the wheel in exchange for some {{slink|Gold Coin|link=Gold Coin (currency)|txt=Gold Coins}}. Winning the "Spin the Wheel!" minigame would allow for the player to gain access to more parts of this stage.

